trans-unit.source: List Service Certificates
trans-unit.target: List Service Certificates

trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>List Service Certificates</languageKeyword> operation lists all of the service certificates associated with the specified cloud service.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>List Service Certificates</languageKeyword> operation lists all of the service certificates associated with the specified cloud service.
